# Interview prep — everything here is User Layer (private per DATA_CONTRACT):
# company research/intel reports AND your filled story-bank with real STAR
# stories. Only the empty story-bank.template.md is tracked, as shared
# scaffolding the system copies to story-bank.md on first use.
interview-prep/*
!interview-prep/story-bank.template.md

